      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/4a30cea6-c755-11e2-ae6b-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
